# VulkanRender v4 procedural many-light deferred demo marker.
#
# The renderer recognizes this extension and builds a procedural scene with:
# - a 100x100 PBR sphere grid
# - 32x32 visible colored light markers
# - a simple room/floor receiver for SSAO and local light falloff
#
# The actual many-light records are generated on the CPU, uploaded to a Vulkan
# storage buffer, and consumed by the v4 deferred composition shader.
